node.text: UPDATE: goldfish were returned! I was told these wouldn’t get large and when I brought them back I was told by another person that the first guy was wrong hahahaha. Thanks for the tips yall. Added some beneficial substrate for the plants and replaced them with a small scoop of tetras. A little experiment in propagation. I feed the fish, the fish shit out their butts and the roots are tickled with fecal joy and in return, so am I.

node.text: I’m designing a flower and flora pressing journal and just got the mock up in! There’s a few changes to make before it’s perfect and I’m gonna discuss those here!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Tyler Thrasher on July 29, 2021. May be an image of book.

node.text:
Hittin ya with another tool for your curiosity. Reservations for the Phantom Flora flower pressing book open up Monday! There will only be 2000 copies available! I don’t imagine we’ll need to order more than that, I’m certain that is plenty for those worried about them selling out! But I’ll keep the bookmakers on notice if so! This can also double as a sketchbook as well with a customizable window for a cover! 
#flowers #floral #flowerpressing #vellum #tylerthrasher

node.text:
Hello citizen scientists! The “Phantom Flora” is done and it’s perfect. I’ve only mentioned this product in passing but I’ve been hard at work on a Flower Pressing journal. Comprised entirely of vellum so you can layer your pressed flora like ghostly layered collages. Each page will include tiny lines to enter simple info such as the contents of the page, date and location the flora was collected. Each journal will also contain a frosted pvc pocket to customize the cover of your flower pressing journal! These are currently in the process of being made and will arrive early November! Just in time for the holidays, however there has been a lot of interest just from the few posts I’ve shared and we’re only releasing 2,000 copies this year. I have a feeling these will go fast and I don’t want anyone to get their hopes up too high on snagging one as a holiday gift too close to the actual holidays so I’m toying with allowing people to reserve their copy a couple of months early! Thoughts?
Also price point is 45USD! I’ll announce when reservations are open!
#thephantomflora #flowerpressing #floral #florists #journal #nature #citizenscientists

node.text:
It time for some more Do Goods. This one is near and dear to my heart. I released a new shirt, the “Hands Off” design aimed at helping kids and teenagers fleeing from abuse and trauma. I’m in talks with Youth Services of Tulsa to see how the money raised from this shirt could help the kids who find shelter and safety with this program. I grew up utilizing their art programs and therapy as a teenager and many ways it saved my life. As of now they offer an array of art therapy based programs including non verbal programs. 100% of the money raised from the “Hands Off” design will go toward funding these therapy programs, and helping these kids on a case by case basis whether that’s through buying clothes, shoes, art supplies, groceries, whatever needs are unmet we want to help. My goal is to raise $5,000 for YST and I’m confident we can do it. I also have two other products made, both featuring my floral scorpion design with gold metallic ink. 100% of THOSE profits will go toward my team, family and my plant problem. The shirts are screenprinted on unisex triblend tees and the poster is screenprinted on 18X24 heavy dark green stock. I’m so effing thrilled with the quality and perfection @flashfloodprint utilizes time and time again, and we wouldn’t be able to bring you cool stuff and raise money for great causes without them. You can preorder your shirts and posters via the shop link in my bio or the shop button on my site tylerthrasher.com or through @dftbarecords 
#tylerthrasher #dftba #dogoodgang #giveback #tulsa

node.text:
Here’s the second illustration for the @rewild “Lost Legends” mission, the Urania sloanus. A supposedly extinct species of moth endemic to Jamaica. The hope is that this species might still exist in some parts of Jamaica and we may be able to reverse its trajectory/ “rediscover” it. Accompanying the illustration are some Jamaican native florals.
#rewild #illustration #science #conservation #nature #jamaica #moth #uraniasloanus

node.text:
GUYS! GOD DAMN!! I have some new killer merch coming your way and as much as I wanted to do a surprise drop, I have to show off the screen print @flashfloodprint did of my floral scorpion design! It’s immaculate. Absolutely perfect. They captured every detail, blade, petal, line, EVERYTHING! Swipe through to see some of the juicy details! These 18X24 posters are huge and are printed with Metallica gold on a dark forest green. Along with these I will drop a shirt with the same gold print and a second design for this summer’s fundraiser/ do good initiative. GAHHHH I’m so fucking happy with these!
#screenprint #scorpion #poster #illustration #nature #science #botany #insects

node.text:
The Thrasher sport was feeling some sort of way and is trying some froggy shit. I’ve never had an entirely albino leaf and whenever these nearly white ones emerge they always fill in with green veining a week or so after unfurling. If this cutting keeps this up we’re looking at a potentially breathtaking plant!
#tylerthrasher #monstera #variegated #houseplants
